{"tid":27023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（選委選舉）非建制派組合名單","createTime":"2016-12-07T05:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T04:57:54.000Z","uid":6604,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9fa0488c8bde567f2fb0c05b4775a63e62d18942","tid":27023,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:29:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/07/132929_ca17bd60461481e08f21d19dfe07a74d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F07%2F132929_ca17bd60461481e08f21d19dfe07a74d.jpg&h=04b0d1ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被視為特首選舉前哨戰的選委選舉，再過4天就投票，扣除已自動當選的界別，逾23萬名功能界別選民近日會陸續收到投票通知卡。<span style=\"color: red;\">選委選舉採多議席多票制（即全票制），每名選民可按所屬界別的選委議席數目，同時投票給多名心水候選人，上限是該界別的議席數目。</span>泛民主派今屆組成「民主300+」多張名單共300多名候選人，強攻14個界別，包括部份梁振英票倉，冀能一舉拿下300個選委議席，為大多數無份投票的香港人爭取籌碼，左右特首選舉大局。《蘋果》羅列出14個界別的「民主300+」候選人名單，及該界別的其他或建制候選人，供讀者參考。<br />\n<br />\n有票的巴絲，請珍惜手上一票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：有票"},{"pid":"4ef48f13a628d699d967d5ea74c0a6a7abe1c998","tid":27023,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:01:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de6ed952be61bbb886d471dca139c8fe8b029a1c","tid":27023,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:07:31.000Z","msg":"法律界個啲點解唔搶盡佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全票制喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有一半票已經屈機啦"},{"pid":"fe5d505c213c92d6e0655b38ee214d79da11ad78","tid":27023,"uid":53932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:16:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>法律界個啲點解唔搶盡佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全票制喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有一半票已經屈機啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無睇新聞?<br />\